<p class="ayah 92-7" id="7" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then We will ease him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلْيُسْرَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">towards [the] ease.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>7<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
