<p class="ayah 92-9" id="9" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَذَّبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And denies</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْحُسْنَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the best,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>9<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
