<p class="ayah 92-19" id="19" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَحَدٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for anyone</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِندَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نِّعْمَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">favor</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُجْزَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to be recompensed</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>19<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
